snippet.title: Poltics & Atheism - Richard Dawkins, Amber Heard, Robyn Blumner -  VIP Arizona 2019
snippet.description:
Atheists have problems in Politics, explains Robyn Blumner at the Richard Dawkins & Amber Heard event in Mesa, Arizona on Oct 16, 2019. Atheists rank behind those convicted of crimes in running for political office, yet there are 535 in Congress and some are silently atheists.
